{"tid":1637694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[核彈無人講]黑警連大肚婆都搞！！！","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:30:49.000Z","uid":8414,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"563d6f9349fe0446e281ac7df1b01591d8371035","tid":1637694,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"From 大肚婆group （請傳！）<br />\n<br />\n尋晚fb影到嗰個大肚婆真係被拉<br />\n唔係啲人「幻想」popo護送大肚婆去醫院咁溫馨<br />\n尋晚由防暴送佢入產前病房<br />\n後來被病房經理請走咗防暴<br />\n而家由一男一女popo守住喺房門口<br />\n仲大大聲講: 佢係「犯」來㗎<br />\n姑娘叫popo出去<br />\n話會嚇親其他太太<br />\n佢地唔走 死守喺病房門口<br />\n<br />\n唔明裡面全部係待產嘅孕婦<br />\n點解可以有男警喺度??<br />\n今時今日癲到連大肚婆都搞<br />\n各位媽媽真係要小心啲!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWAdEzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWAdEzy.jpg&h=4eaf36b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/occupyingtrend/photos/a.583178241793776/2188859071225677?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foccupyingtrend%2Fphotos%2Fa.583178241793776%2F2188859071225677%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=508ec411\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/occupyingtrend/photos/a.583178241793776/2188859071225677?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連準爸爸都唔可入既產前病房點解可以有男警守？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n快d share 俾bk老母知！！！"},{"pid":"afd5ebe05ea0a857d36364e482bdd0d4ddabbf58","tid":1637694,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"文宣快入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91798a619f3c63098e47a256deccb1392aa5fb4d","tid":1637694,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"Airdrop俾d 同溫層知！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=